channel.title: Error_game_js5connect
channel.description: Hello, I have expireance with runescape private servers in the past, but recently I have gotten back into working with these servers, also recently (and this has never happened before) I have been getting this error message on the client promp that says 'error_game_js5connect', also at the same time the loading screen freezes at 'loading title screen - 0%'. Again, I have had expireance with Runescape private servers before but I am still pretty new at it. Lastly, and this may not be related, but when I try to login to a server via Moparscape.org, I can't log in and I get this message that says, "Unexpected Server Response Please Try Using A Different World". I am using a 614 source. cache 614, and QROOT Client-Source. I have googled and looked up the same error and this site and youtube but I havn't been able to find anything that has solved the problem, please help! :confused:
